{"tid":2315730,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國房企倒閉潮來了！至10月底已453家房企宣布破產","createTime":"2020-12-07T11:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T01:45:34.000Z","uid":141151,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1d38ca4004a1d0e7d255f84070b964ec17d60e4d","tid":2315730,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:12:54.000Z","msg":"中國房企倒閉潮來了！至10月底已453家房企宣布破產<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3373432\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3373432&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTgOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=ebec2d84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3373432&h=ca38b96e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3373432</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國房市泡沫化速度加劇，即使不斷有一、二級城市宣稱房價上漲，但是，根據中國財經媒體的追蹤，2020年到10月底止，全中國共有全國共453家房企宣布破產，平均每天約1.5家被清算。業界預測，中國之前高槓桿投資的房產企業，持續近20年的高速增長即將劃下休止符。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">綜合中媒報導，中共中央從2016年底決定打房、擊退房市炒家後，一步步加緊對開發商的管控，但效果明顯不佳，不過今年武漢肺炎疫情的衝擊，房屋銷售去化困難，只能邊降價邊賣，在今年雙十一促銷檔各大房企更卯足勁降價求賣，但除少數大咖房企還有一點成績之外，大部分都只能嘆息。<br />\n<br />\n房企減量推案，但是去化壓力仍壓的房企喘不過氣努力「求活」，不斷的在海內外發新債還舊債，據統計，今年前3季，房企發債規模刷新歷史紀錄，海內外債券發行307次，融資規模約3,247億元人民幣（下同，約1.36兆台幣），年增長14%，每家房企都想搶在政策窗口期內融資。<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n不過，中共中央更加緊管控力道，今年8月畫出「三道紅線」卡住房企，本月3日中共國務院副總理韓正召開會議，再強調打房態度，再定位「房子是用來住的、不是用來炒」。<br />\n<br />\n所謂中共中央針對房企的「三道紅線」，即房企剔除預收款後的資產負債率需大於70%、淨負債率大於100%、短期借款不得超過現金儲備。"},{"pid":"1d861a8a55053faecf56cb26d2ac3138098a6245","tid":2315730,"uid":300006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:14:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />you are fake news<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6337351aca8558c4d3dcb7496f95b19af8018d5a","tid":2315730,"uid":337444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:14:23.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f33bf86ebf755bef74ee8ab2380c3eb3c85625","tid":2315730,"uid":293332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:15:44.000Z","msg":"中國或又成大贏家"},{"pid":"fd816ceed6457de1829e55adeebd108baf9a2ccf","tid":2315730,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:16:50.000Z","msg":"唔怕 仲有六萬幾間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08fd14e27a3eebca8c74f5c4106fbb10e7a6ee8b","tid":2315730,"uid":173271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:17:04.000Z","msg":"咩規模先<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大6好多自己開d細鋪仔又話自己搞生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec5124ef739cc705c1f9de54d9e2ad8a61880a14","tid":2315730,"uid":383301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:17:25.000Z","msg":"若然屬實"},{"pid":"023f4317b664ae3e43ba3b98044d2fda4fd3b4fc","tid":2315730,"uid":191474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:18:30.000Z","msg":"中國又是最後的贏家"},{"pid":"172e17aa2372aab9464b0b3fec9327be28cf8229","tid":2315730,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:19:41.000Z","msg":"沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8232344de3ca7951d7a97084efd5c91ffc5ad927","tid":2315730,"uid":8880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:19:42.000Z","msg":"最後咩事都冇<br />\n欠韭菜d錢就由佢<br />\n叫國家還錢 你都on9<br />\n差國家錢 成家都有危險"},{"pid":"c3f2196cb61c7c7d35fd8a85d4a702a259ae1fce","tid":2315730,"uid":126683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:20:38.000Z","msg":"GPA gogogo la"},{"pid":"4f5931adad9ff5d2e492175d8190bc688f58fa28","tid":2315730,"uid":380132,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:20:40.000Z",